r relies on the C++ preset bind path to flip `rectangleCornerRadiiIndependent` (see `_bindKeyframeExpressionToParameterField`).\n- amount: For type=roundIn/roundOut, the target radius in px.\n- *StartFrame / *EndFrame: For type=custom, the per-corner start/end radii. Only the pair matching the current `corner` selection is animated.\n- delay / duration / easing: Shared timing for the animation.',le=[{name:"type",type:s2.J0O.TEXT,label:"motion.preset_flyout.type",defaultText:"roundIn",selectConfig:{options:[{value:"roundIn",label:"motion.preset_flyout.corner_radius.type.round_in"},{value:"roundOut",label:"motion.preset_flyout.corner_radius.type.round_out"},{value:"custom",label:"motion.preset_flyout.type.custom"}]}},{name:"corner",type:s2.J0O.TEXT,label:"motion.preset_flyout.corner_radius.corner",defaultText:"all",selectConfig:{options:[{value:"all",label:"motion.preset_flyout.corner_radius.corner.all"},{value:"topLeft",label:"motion.preset_flyout.corner_radius.corner.top_left"},{value:"topRight",label:"motion.preset_flyout.corner_radius.corner.top_right"},{value:"bottomLeft",label:"motion.preset_flyout.corner_radius.corner.bottom_left"},{value:"bottomRight",label:"motion.preset_flyout.corner_radius.corner.bottom_right"}]}},{name:"amount",type:s2.J0O.NUMBER,label:"motion.preset_flyout.amount",defaultNumber:10,inputConfig:{min:0,unit:"px"}},{name:"allStartFrame",type:s2.J0O.NUMBER,label:"motion.preset_flyout.start_frame",defaultNumber:10,inputConfig:{min:0,unit:"px",icon:"radius_all"}},{name:"allEndFrame",type:s2.J0O.NUMBER,label:"motion.preset_flyout.end_frame",defaultNumber:0,inputConfig:{min:0,unit:"px",icon:"radius_all"}},{name:"topLeftStartFrame",type:s2.J0O.NUMBER,label:"motion.preset_flyout.start_frame",defaultNumber:0,inputConfig:{min:0,unit:"px",icon:"radius_top_left"}},{name:"topLeftEndFrame",type:s2.J0O.NUMBER,label:"motion.preset_flyout.end_frame",defaultNumber:20,inputConfig:{min:0,unit:"px",icon:"radius_top_left"}},{name:"topRightStartFrame",type:s2.J0O.